Classes/SSProbabilityDistributions.html.name: SSProbabilityDistributions
Classes/SSProbabilityDistributions.html.abstract: Provides some of the commonest probability distributions. In general, functions are prefixed by pdf, cdf, quantile for probability density function, cumulative density function and inverse cumulative density function respectively. Probablity distributions in general are defined in relatively narrow conditions expressed in terms of certain parameters such as degree of freedom, shape or mean. Sometimes it is possible, that a particular distribution isn’t defined for a parameter provided.
